About the source code:
The source for the norton guide clone is complete except for the following
units:
YNSYSTEM
YNCRT
YNDOS
STRINT
SWAPOPUP
SWAPVARS

I can't release these units because of some copyright resonse.
SWAPOPUP and SWAPVARS are units which implement the TSR swapping part. It's
completly written by me a few years back. The TPU version can only write the
HEAP to XMS,EMS or file.
NGHELP.EXE is linked with the complete version and leaves only a 4 kb part
in memory.

